T1  - Washington Policy Analysts and the Propagation of Political Information
AU  - Bradley, Daniel
AU  - Gokkaya, Sinan
AU  - Liu, Xi
AU  - Michaely, Roni
Y1  - 2023/10/26
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2024/08/01
